# 🔹 3. Microsoft Graph – Le cœur de l’automatisation

Microsoft Graph permet d’automatiser :

- Entra ID (users, groups, devices)  
- Intune (apps, policies, compliance, devices)  
- Autopilot (profils, devices, imports)  
- MDE (exclusions, onboarding, actions)  
- Teams, SharePoint, Exchange, etc.  

Authentification :

```powershell
Connect-MgGraph -Scopes "Device.ReadWrite.All","User.ReadWrite.All","Group.ReadWrite.All"
Select-MgProfile -Name beta
 Graph = API unifiée de tout l’écosystème Microsoft 365.
4. Exemples de scripts utiles (à ajouter dans ce dossier)
✔️ 1) Lister les devices Intune

Connect-MgGraph -Scopes "Device.Read.All"
Select-MgProfile beta

Get-MgDeviceManagementManagedDevice |
    Select-Object deviceName, userPrincipalName, operatingSystem, complianceState

2) Importer un Hardware Hash Autopilot via Graph
Connect-MgGraph -Scopes "DeviceManagementServiceConfig.ReadWrite.All"
Select-MgProfile beta

Import-MgDeviceManagementWindowsAutopilotDeviceIdentity -InputFile "C:\HWID\AutopilotHWID.csv"
3) Créer un groupe dynamique Entra ID
Connect-MgGraph -Scopes "Group.ReadWrite.All"
Select-MgProfile beta

New-MgGroup -DisplayName "W11-Autopilot" `
            -MailEnabled:$false `
            -MailNickname "W11-Autopilot" `
            -SecurityEnabled:$true `
            -GroupTypes "DynamicMembership" `
            -MembershipRule "(device.deviceOSType -eq ""Windows"") -and (device.deviceOSVersion -startsWith ""10.0.2"")" `
            -MembershipRuleProcessingState "On"
✔️ 4) Lister les applications Win32 Intune
Connect-MgGraph -Scopes "DeviceManagementApps.Read.All"
Select-MgProfile beta

Get-MgDeviceAppManagementMobileApp |
    Where-Object { $_.'@odata.type' -eq "#microsoft.graph.win32LobApp" } |
    Select-Object displayName, description, publisher, isFeatured
✔️ 5) Déclencher une action MDE (ex : isolation)
Connect-MgGraph -Scopes "ThreatHunting.ReadWrite.All"
Select-MgProfile beta

Invoke-MgSecurityDeviceAction -DeviceId "<ID>" -Action "isolate"

Ces scripts montrent que tu sais automatiser Intune, Autopilot, Entra ID et MDE.

